<div id="clusterExplorerHelpText">
    <h1>Welcome to the cluster manager</h1>

    <p>
    For managing clusters, follow these instructions:
    <ul>
        <li>Use the "add cluster" Button to create a cluster</li>
        <li>Use the search column on the right hand side to find and select items</li>
        <li>
            associate items with the cluster by dragging them into the centered container or onto the cluster tree
            node
        </li>
        <li>Double-click on a tree node to open the cluster detail view</li>
        <li>Change the hierarchical structure of the cluster tree by dragging tree nodes</li>
        <li>All updates are saved automatically</li>
    </ul>
    </p>


</div>